==English==

===Etymology===
From {{confix|xeno|phobe|lang=en}}. From {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|ξένος||foreign, strange}}, + {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|φόβος||fear}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˈzinəfoʊb/|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# One who [[fear]]s that which is [[unknown]]; one who fears [[people]] who are [[different]] from [[oneself]], [[especially]] [[foreigner]]s.

